			dependencies: ["7A04000000000102"]
			description: [
				"&8[ SYSTEM ANALYSIS — AUTONOMY ]&r"
				""
				"&7It does not wait for instructions any more. Given a pattern, it acts. The system rebuilds whatever it is missing, on its own.&r"
				""
				"&8I recovered a partial index while it worked. Fragments of a record we were not meant to keep.&r"
			]
