			description: [
				"&8[ SYSTEM ANALYSIS — FABRICATION ]&r"
				""
				"&7The system does not just recall. It&r &8makes&r&7. Given a recipe and materials, it fabricates on request. The Crafting Unit is the recovered heart of that process.&r"
				""
				"&8Objective: build a Crafting CPU — a Crafting Unit, a 1k Storage, an Accelerator — and a Storage Bus to feed it.&r"
