		{
			dependencies: ["7A04000000000105"]
			description: [
				"&8[ SYSTEM ANALYSIS — ONE MIND ]&r"
				""
				"&7The network does not think in places. A point here is a point there. The recovered tunnels carry anything — items, power, even signals — between two ends as if the space between were folded away.&r"
				""
				"&8Objective: expand capacity and reach — a 16k cell, a P2P tunnel, a Level Emitter to let the system act on its own.&r"
			]
