			description: [
				"&8[ SYSTEM ANALYSIS — BEYOND THE NETWORK ]&r"
				""
				"&7The last recovered schematics stop describing storage and start describing&r &8space&r&7. A ring that links networks across any distance. A field that stores a room inside a block. This is where their engineering and their&r &8other&r &7research begin to look like the same thing.&r"
				""
				"&8Objective: build a Quantum Network Bridge (Ring + Link) and a Spatial IO Port.&r"
