			dependencies: ["7A04000000000102"]
			description: [
				"&8[ RECOVERED SYSTEM — IT STILL RUNS ]&r"
				""
				"&7Not every machine they left is silent. Some of the recovered terminals still boot. They wait for input. They expect an operator who is not coming.&r"
				""
				"&8Objective: build a working computer — a Computer, a Disk Drive, a Monitor, a wireless Modem. See what it still remembers how to do.&r"
				""
				"&8On a booted terminal, type&r &farchive&r&8. For the sealed records, leave recovered media in the attached drive.&r"
